{"tid":1142293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中$4000萬巨獎男淪落街頭 涉盜用銀行卡買彩票","createTime":"2019-05-07T03:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T05:46:26.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"601982a83170d3e2d6ef2c0f55ab23fb51d9d42b","tid":1142293,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apUzAWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapUzAWe.png&h=c4106788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古德拉姆（左）及沃森(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1X10ob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1X10ob.png&h=b2d7e88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古德拉姆被發現淪落街頭(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n英國博爾頓（Bolton）兩名中了彩票巨獎的男子，因被懷疑盜用銀行卡買彩票，博彩公司拒絕向兩人發放獎金。他們中獎後一度大肆慶祝，但至今仍未獲派彩，其中一人更被發現淪落街頭。<br />\n<br />\n36歲的古德拉姆（Mark Goodram）與31歲的友人沃森（Jon-Ross Watson）上月中彩票，贏得400萬鎊（約4,100萬港元）的獎金。不過，博彩公司Camelot懷疑他們是用偷回來的銀行卡買彩票，於是決定調查事件，其間不會給予任何獎金。由於銀行只會發卡給戶口持有人，而古德拉姆及沃森兩人都沒有戶口，理論上不會持有銀行卡。兩人否認偷卡，並解釋指他們向一名叫約翰（John）的朋友給予現金，要他用銀行卡代買彩票。<br />\n<br />\n雖然未拿到獎金，但兩人已開始大肆慶祝。他們早前到倫敦玩樂，還分別上載了手持大量50鎊鈔票和酒瓶的照片。但有報道指，古德拉姆在周五被發現身處街頭，喝着一罐罐蘋果酒，進食瑞典肉丸充飢，據指他是被室友趕離住所。<br />\n<br />\n古德拉姆一名朋友說：「你聽過由貧窮到富有的故事。但他由過着開香檳的生活，認為自己是百萬富翁，去到要淪落街頭，喝着平價的蘋果酒、與乞丐為伍。他在中獎前是剛出獄不久，但他已被趕出家園，過着最痛苦的日子。他真的感到很沮喪，他仍相信自己會拿到錢，又說如果Camelot不付錢，他會告上法庭。」<br />\n<br />\n古德拉姆及沃森兩人都有犯罪記錄。古德拉姆去年涉嫌偷竊被判監8個月，他中獎時才剛出獄數天；沃森去年因盜用銀行卡被判囚16周。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"82cd068cd0c40a19f817f9fcf1509f9c44052d7e","tid":1142293,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"拍得電影"},{"pid":"3c18d4f57ef481739ab64a323c24a0b0cc4c9597","tid":1142293,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"我都想試下進食瑞典肉丸充飢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bee7543818bcccd87fcc4e15d099c9751702e84","tid":1142293,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"未收錢先洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9c426250d3fe580b8eea6c9dcd5c1588e23aec","tid":1142293,"uid":28279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"博彩公司就係咁仆街，成日借啲意唔派彩自己袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a52e1a2bf88228d52610e56eebc5bd99b3cba3c","tid":1142293,"uid":29613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"件T 仲要寫住Most Wanted <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716cf183d2c331723ecd14d70a3b062cf1e83c90","tid":1142293,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9c426250d3fe580b8eea6c9dcd5c1588e23aec","tid":1142293,"uid":28279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"博彩公司就係咁仆街，成日借啲意唔派彩自己袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d689b2b07782b5f891f278efa37d6e8315111d","tid":1142293,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a52e1a2bf88228d52610e56eebc5bd99b3cba3c","tid":1142293,"uid":29613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"件T 仲要寫住Most Wanted <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f43792349936bcbe635cd7c232d6b1650b1d898","tid":1142293,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"